ApplyCertificate.document: This API is used to apply for a free certificate.
ApplyCertificate.name: Applies for a free certificate

CancelCertificateOrder.document: This API is used to cancel a certificate order.
CancelCertificateOrder.name: Cancels a certificate order

CommitCertificateInformation.document: This API is used to submit a certificate order.
CommitCertificateInformation.name: Submits a certificate order

DeleteCertificate.document: This API is used to delete a certificate.
DeleteCertificate.name: Deletes a certificate

DescribeCertificate.document: This API is used to obtain certificate information.
DescribeCertificate.name: Obtains certificate information

DescribeCertificateDetail.document: This API is used to obtain certificate details.
DescribeCertificateDetail.name: Obtains certificate details

DescribeCertificateOperateLogs.document: This API is used to obtain certificate operation logs in the current account.
DescribeCertificateOperateLogs.name: Obtains certificate operation logs

DescribeCertificates.document: This API is used to obtain the certificate list.
DescribeCertificates.name: Obtains the certificate list

DownloadCertificate.document: This API is used to download a certificate.
DownloadCertificate.name: Downloads a certificate

ModifyCertificateAlias.document: This API is used to modify certificate alias by inputting the certificate ID and new alias.
ModifyCertificateAlias.name: Modifies a certificate alias

ModifyCertificateProject.document: This API is used to modify the projects of multiple certificates.
ModifyCertificateProject.name: Modifies the projects of multiple certificates

ReplaceCertificate.document: This API is used to reissue a certificate. Note that if you have applied for a free certificate, only an RSA-2048 certificate will be reissued, and the certificate can be reissued only once.
ReplaceCertificate.name: Reissues a certificate

SubmitCertificateInformation.document: This API is used to submit certificate information.
SubmitCertificateInformation.name: Submits certificate information

UploadCertificate.document: This API is used to upload a certificate.
UploadCertificate.name: Uploads a certificate
